Kelly, I hope you made it back to the US without issues. I am with my mothe=
r in Munich, Germany - going back to NL by train on Monday. It was great see=
ing you, and in particular sharing one or the other panel, meeting, and pres=
entation with you =F0=9F=98=8A



Attached a request for IAWN membership from Klet. Since I haven't seen Tim =
distributing it, I wanted it to forward to you to coordinate who would distr=
ibute this to the IAWN steering group.



Needless to say that I fully support their application - they use their 1 m=
 telescope exclusively for NEO follow-up, and are in the business longer tha=
n I can think.



dvk




